
This repository contains the solutions and analysis focused on DFT and window functions using MATLAB.

Contents
Problem Definition:

The detailed problem description is provided in Problem_definition.pdf. This outlines the tasks involving sinusoid signal analysis, FFT normalization, frequency domain exploration, and the impact of window functions.
Report:

The file Report.docx contains detailed responses to the questions, observations, and results, including:
Frequency domain plots.
Analysis of leakage and amplitude changes.
Effects of applying various window functions.
MATLAB Code:

The MATLAB scripts used for:
Generating sinusoidal signals.
Performing FFT analysis.
Exploring the impact of window functions.
Includes well-commented code for reproducibility.
